_sText:
This is a remix of an old map.
Since I didn't find the old map when I felt nostalgic, I decided to make a remix of the map.
If you find any buggs, please leave a comment below :)

The map contains; bomb site, buyzone, different camp spots, speed surfing, jail etc etc.

Credits to the creator of surf_bomb_board for the ideas!

Keep in mind that I didn't steal his map, I made it from scratch
